{"tid":1873390,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【痴撚線】佢哋運咗十萬個口罩返嚟派","createTime":"2020-02-10T15:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T16:21:51.000Z","uid":231886,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"4d2b24ce426a4236c8fc37139a0933d6ad617bc5","tid":1873390,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T15:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">痴撚線架佢哋！<br />\n仲要免費派？<br />\n香港人真係好痴線！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有片有文有圖</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉至：<a href=\"https://t.me/projectr4hky\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fprojectr4hky&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4fS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=0b377b2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/projectr4hky</a><br />\n<br />\n#ProjectR #十萬口罩計劃<br />\n<br />\n你哋最期待嘅事出現喇！<br />\n合資格人士請密切留意Project R公佈！<br />\n<br />\n============================<br />\n【10萬個口罩順利抵港 免費派發至弱勢社群】<br />\n<br />\n#ProjectR 喺世界各地嘅香港人幫助之下，成功採購了10萬個口罩，並喺今日終於運抵香港完成查收！我地將會在各區區議員協調之下，盡快派發予弱勢社群。記得留意我地最新嘅資訊。香港人支持住！祝醫護平安，祝香港人平安。<br />\n<br />\n是次口罩派發之合資格人士︰<br />\n1. 65歲以上<br />\n2. 7歲以上、14歲以下小童<br />\n3. 孕婦及其配偶<br />\n4. 長期病患者 <br />\n5. 食環署清潔工（包括外判工人）<br />\n<br />\n每位合資格人士獲派10個口罩<br />\n<br />\n口罩規格︰Surgical masks with 99% BFE.   <br />\n供應商及品牌: Emerald Professional Protection Products<br />\n產品資料：<a href=\"https://www.emeraldppp.com/99-bfe-filtration-surgical-procedure-masks/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.emeraldppp.com%2F99-bfe-filtration-surgical-procedure-masks%2F&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4fS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=cb547feb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.emeraldppp.com/99-bfe-filtration-surgical-procedure-masks/</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nFollow US<br />\nFacbook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ProjectRforHKY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FProjectRforHKY%2F&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4fS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=d1a77fbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ProjectRforHKY/</a><br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/projectrforhky?igshid=bywb6yll4dq6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fprojectrforhky%3Figshid%3Dbywb6yll4dq6&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4fS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=86490ed9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/projectrforhky?igshid=bywb6yll4dq6</a><br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://t.me/projectr4hky\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fprojectr4hky&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4fS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=0b377b2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/projectr4hky</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nProject R 是一個開放而包容的平台，目標是構建屬於全球香港人的社區及經濟共同體（Ecosystem)，連接各行業，本地和海外的香港人，甚至世界各地支持香港人的民眾，形成一個透過網絡連結的新群體。平台以「香港人__香港人」為主軸，中間留白，讓香港人發揮想像力和創意，一齊推出各種項目及計劃，將彼此之間連結起來，形成共力，為這個Ecosystem 注入不同的內容及活力。<br />\n<br />\n#ProjectR #武漢肺炎 #港人優先 #口罩難求 #免費口罩 #香港人 #黃色經濟圈<br />\n#唔靠政府 #香港人靠香港人 #2盒thanks"},{"pid":"88f463fc6b285a7ca3c605ca009f796633be357f","tid":1873390,"uid":231886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T15:47:13.000Z","msg":"和你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af504f931d4b793c879d7a1a0667a397dc6e5d9d","tid":1873390,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T15:47:36.000Z","msg":"和你二推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm